    <usageGuidance>Problems with architectures, and systems, can be quite complex. Ensure that the problem is clearly understood, since&#xD;
sometimes the issue at first blush is not the issue at all. Refine the problem definition and do&amp;nbsp;a thorough analysis.&#xD;
Impacts may also be obscure; look at the system from multiple perspectives, and perhaps do a walk-through of the process(s)&#xD;
if necessary.</usageGuidance>
  </org.eclipse.epf.uma:ActivityDescription>
