  <org.eclipse.epf.uma:DescriptorDescription xmi:id="-mzAf0LTXaUWr8Ddz2LkDmg" name="ea_define_ad_tech,_FDwdYd8aEdynr9jlfK-aMA" guid="-mzAf0LTXaUWr8Ddz2LkDmg">
    <usageGuidance>Architectural Decisions may be defined at any time during the development of the Technical Perspective. ADs are typically&#xD;
at the heart of the main aspects of the Technical level models. In effect, the transition from the Logical level models to&#xD;
the Technical level models is defined by the set of ADs defined.</usageGuidance>
    <refinedDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
