&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    See: &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot; href=&quot;./../../UAM/guidances/termdefinitions/uam_business_model_2878FB14.html&quot;&#xD;
    guid=&quot;_ka0YEMI9EeKSedlRPHdUIQ&quot;>Term Definition: Business Model&lt;/a>&#xD;
&lt;/p></refinedDescription>
  </org.eclipse.epf.uma:DescriptorDescription>
  <org.eclipse.epf.uma:DescriptorDescription xmi:id="-bIpH9b1ZPscoQzr-lsQgVA" name="uam_in_business-objective,_ROOP06sTEeSFIOC-Wm7nrA" guid="-bIpH9b1ZPscoQzr-lsQgVA">
    <refinedDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Business Objectives are an input to many UAM based IT Architecture activities and tasks. They are is created by&#xD;
    business experts within the enterprise.&amp;nbsp; See the overview of inputs here: &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../UAM/customcategories/uam_inputs_82560214.html&quot; guid=&quot;_UauIAGtMEeS7ieerwXbTqg&quot;>Inputs&lt;/a>.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    See:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot; href=&quot;./../../UAM/deliveryprocesses/uam_ent_planning_1D88CE12.html&quot;&#xD;
    guid=&quot;_iTW2kK8KEeSUf-NO_1Ayag&quot;>Activity: Enterprise Planning&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;and &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../UAM/deliveryprocesses/uam_gate-0_6529D84.html&quot; guid=&quot;_nfG7AK8QEeSUf-NO_1Ayag&quot;>Milestone: Gate 0&lt;/a>.&#xD;
